# 9. 線路の向こう

Ichika: The tracks seem to extend towards that starry sky...
Ichika: That's incredible... I didn't realize a place like this existed in SEKAI...
Miku: We believe it's an entirely new area that appeared recently, rather than a place that's always existed.
Ichika: A new area...?
Miku: Yes. We understand that you and the others' feelings made it appear.
Miku: Until just a minute ago, I'd been wondering what those feelings entailed...
Miku: But you gave me the answer to that question, Ichika.
Ichika: Huh?
Miku: Why do you think this place appeared, Ichika?
Ichika: Why...?
Miku: Hehe. It may not be entirely obvious to you right now.
Miku: But I believe you'll figure out the answer.
Ichika: You do...?
Ichika: Huh? I'm hearing footsteps...
???: Hurry, you guys!
???: D-Don't run so fast! It's not safe!
???: See? She's getting way too excited again...
???: Huff... Huff... Everyone, wait for me...
Ichika: Are those kids?
Ichika: But what are they doing here...?
???: Wow! Look at the stars! They're so pretty!
???: They really are. And it's rare for the sky to be so clear like this.
???: Oh, these tracks... They go up towards the sky... Does that mean this train can fly?
???: What?! That's so cool! Then, wanna try boarding it?! It might take us closer to those stars!
???: You're daydreaming again... But I guess we could go on it for a little bit.
???: *Nod* I'm a little scared, but...
Ichika: (Those kids...)
Ichika: (They kind of remind me of us when we were little...)
???: Don't worry! We're all boarding it at the same time!
???: We'll be able to go wherever we want as long as we stick together!
???: Hehe... You saying that makes it feel true.
???: Yeah...!
???: I wanna go too. Us. Together. Wherever we want...!
Ichika: Oh...
Ichika: (Going wherever you want together...)
Miku: Those kids are just like you and the others, Ichika.
Ichika: Yeah...
Ichika: I decided that I wanted to be with the others and become professional musicians together.
Ichika: (But when we first started, we were the furthest thing from good...)
Ichika: (And I was so nervous about performing in front of other people that I had a lot of trouble singing...)
Ichika: (But I didn't run. I kept trying, practiced like there was no tomorrow...)
Ichika: (And we've been able to make it this far together as a result.)
Ichika: But we can't stop here...
Ichika: We have to keep moving forward. As far as we can. Even up among those stars.
Ichika: I want to see what it's like up there with them.
Ichika: Oh...
Ichika: Are these the feelings you were talking about, Miku...?
Miku: Yes, I think you're in the right neighborhood...
Ichika: If that's the case... Then I really want to go.
Ichika: The four of us. Together. To the stars at the end of these tracks.
Miku: I'm sure you'll be able to, Ichika.
Miku: Wherever you want. As far as you like.
Ichika: Thanks, Miku.
Ichika: (I wonder what it's like beyond the stars at the end of these tracks.)
Ichika: (I really have no idea right now...)
Ichika: (But I'm going to keep doing my best so that we get to keep moving forward together.)
